{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"35fd37c3d3","title":"对高级步兵学校政治队第二期教育计划的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8c5f254e86","index":0,"year":1953,"month":6,"day":4,"articleId":"35fd37c3d3"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"faf3592984","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"35fd37c3d3","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭德怀，当时任人民革命军事委员会副主席。"},{"id":"1d8975c716","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"35fd37c3d3","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指人民革命军事委员会总政治部军校管理部1953年5月1日制订的中国人民解放军高级步兵学校政治队第二期教育计划。"},{"id":"dd5b73d56c","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"35fd37c3d3","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东对这个教育计划稿作了三处修改：一是将训练要求的第一条“加强马克思列宁主义、毛泽东思想的教育”一句话中的“毛泽东思想”五个字删去：二是将这一条中“了解由新民主主义过渡到社会主义的条件和道路”一句，改为“了解由新民主主义逐步地过渡到社会主义的条件和道路”；三是在“每天学习时间定为九小时半：正课六小时：复习射击教练、队列教练一小时：自习二小时半”一句中的“九小时半”处划了横线和问号，并在旁边批注：“似以八小时为好，即正课五小时，操练一小时，自习二小时。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0808a1c946","type":"title","text":"对高级步兵学校政治队第二期教育计划的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"35fd37c3d3"},{"id":"faf3592984","type":"paragraph","text":"彭德怀同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"35fd37c3d3"},{"id":"1d8975c716","type":"paragraph","text":"此件还你。未细看，望了一下，有几处修改。另关于每天九小时半学习时间，似太多，改为八小时如何？无其夏天，学生吃不消。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"35fd37c3d3"},{"id":"dd5b73d56c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"35fd37c3d3"},{"id":"28a3c9745e","type":"paragraph","text":"六月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"35fd37c3d3"}],"page":{"id":"48d371bf9a","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"35fd37c3d3","start":193,"end":193}}}},"__N_SSG":true}